          <h2 id="real-numbers">Example: 2-Bedroom Downtown Toronto Condo</h2>
          <p>Let's put real numbers to this. Say you own a 2-bedroom condo in downtown Toronto and rent it for $3,000/month. That is $36,000/year gross.</p>

